    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. but i'm worried about that \"double-edged sword\" thing. if i'm in a small town where everyone's already on a tight budget, raising my prices might just kill my business. is there any actual evidence that the \"better staff\" thing actually offsets the higher payroll, or is that just something people say to make the hikes sound okay?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
